{"tid":1018673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港女權婦團無哂聲氣系列4】沙特app監控女性行蹤","createTime":"2019-02-12T11:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T13:03:31.000Z","uid":54337,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"23362b08a106025a29599826629cdc64f1fbc4b6","tid":1018673,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:47:39.000Z","msg":"沙特app監控女性行蹤<br />\n<br />\n沙特阿拉伯法例規定，女性必須有一名合法男性監護人，當地政府開發名為Absher的手機app(圖)，當女性使用護照時，該app便會傳送警報短訊給男性監護人，讓其掌握受監管女性的行蹤，令她們難以逃出國外。該app可在蘋果iTunes及Google Play下載，至今下載次數逾100萬，早前沙特少女逃至加拿大的事件令其廣受注意，人權監察及國際特赦組織指其侵犯人權及歧視女性，並批評蘋果及Google成為幫兇，助長沙特政府執行「性別隔離」。"},{"pid":"6332b9bd98f0e28309248bc3c0de683eb17c4eaf","tid":1018673,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:47:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9app%E7%9B%A3%E6%8E%A7%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E8%A1%8C%E8%B9%A4-161108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2589%25B9app%25E7%259B%25A3%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2580%25A7%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25B9%25A4-161108&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIuiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=f167f51f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9app%E7%9B%A3%E6%8E%A7%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E8%A1%8C%E8%B9%A4-161108</a>"},{"pid":"d3d361da1bd8807a3b83b1c16390af2e4389df6a","tid":1018673,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"香港班女權婦團呢？<br />\nSlut walk 呢？"},{"pid":"686c43e239a661d32a295be2adfd35955841a1c0","tid":1018673,"uid":54337,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"印度女人無權入神廟，香港女權婦團唔出聲。<br />\n沙特少女卡農逃婚，香港女權婦團唔出聲。<br />\n南韓女運動員被性侵犯，香港女權婦團唔出聲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐美女權婦團搞slut walk，呂麗瑤告教練唔成，香港女權婦團就照跟，覺得潮in型，自我感覺良好"},{"pid":"7ecc210360c100420490568d8e7ea7e6fae9c9f2","tid":1018673,"uid":54337